title: Eva Malečková
text:
Hello!
I am a trained biologist (yes, I know how pipetting goes and what is usual composition of a PCR reaction) who developed an interest into genomics early on. Any kind of “-omics” goes hand in hand with big data, data analysis and visualization. Here it was - my new passion and further career developments until my current role of a Scientific Associate at Resolve Biosciences (Monheim, Germany).
